  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the diced onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the diced red bell pepper and cook for an additional 2-3 minutes.",
    "Add the diced aji amarillo pepper and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the quinoa, water, tomatoes, vinegar, namul-blanch-season, and saffron to the skillet.",
    "Stir to combine, then bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low, cover, and simmer for 20-25 minutes or until the quinoa is tender and the liquid has been absorbed.",
    "Stir in the ricotta salata cheese until melted and well combined.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Transfer the paella to a serving dish and garnish with chopped cilantro.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy!"
  ],
